
📌 Responsive Website Project
This is a modern, responsive website designed to showcase a clean and user-friendly interface. The project focuses on visual appeal, smooth navigation, and accessibility across various screen sizes. It was built using Bootstrap, ensuring fast development and responsive design out of the box.

🎯 Features
Fully responsive layout (mobile, tablet, desktop)

Hero section with prominent call-to-action

About section with text and image layout

Services or features section with icons/cards

Team section with team member profiles

Contact section with form or contact info

Smooth scrolling and consistent design language

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3

Bootstrap 5

JavaScript (for interactivity)

